cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as machine translation and post-editing. Additionally, the use of neural networks and attention mechanisms suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus on training and evaluating the model on specific datasets suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of artificial data and the potential for image captioning applications suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
